{"tid":1105892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫委會仲以為自己不敗","createTime":"2019-04-14T08:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T00:54:10.000Z","uid":8909,"like":15,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c10135b833c2ef8ef11f45857b8b2cacf8c9002c","tid":1105892,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"其實醫委會驚到瀨屎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民建制謀合作　收回醫委權力 由立會修例放寬引入海外醫生<br />\n【本報訊】醫委會早前否決豁免有限度註冊海外醫生實習的所有方案，被立法會多個黨派追擊。醫委會主席劉允怡前日回應說：「佢哋唔滿意，咪立法囉，攞返（醫委會）一部份權力，攞返全部權力囉！」民建聯及民主黨馬上響應，昨日表示會提出私人條例草案，修訂《醫生註冊條例》，放寬引入海外醫生。其中民主黨要求醫委會增加非業界代表委員，及引入類似新加坡的海外醫生免試執業模式。公共醫療醫生協會表示，醫生專業自主受《基本法》保障。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655776?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655776%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=a881f001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655776%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=d0f1b19f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655776?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐遭炒作　委員擬聯署提早表決<br />\n【本報訊】醫委會本月3日否決豁免有限度註冊專科海外醫生實習的所有方案，其後被不同政黨立法會議員追擊。醫委會原定下月8日開會再表決方案，據悉，有醫委會委員擬發動聯署，要求醫委會召開緊急會議，希望提早開會，加快解決海外醫生實習問題，以免事件繼續發酵，成為被炒作及混淆公眾視聽的藉口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655778&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8kVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=9ea96ae7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655778&h=012757b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655778</a>"},{"pid":"44ed3d94ffbcad46d65cf1b50cd10f65827e027e","tid":1105892,"uid":202698,"like":74,"dislike":22,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"香港公立醫療水平基本上係第三世界級數<br />\n醫醫相衛已經係公開既事實"},{"pid":"16ed948fbd1ca51bfea9b1230408fb4dffc44dbc","tid":1105892,"uid":11148,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"劉允怡前日回應說：「佢哋唔滿意，咪立法囉，攞返（醫委會）一部份權力，攞返全部權力囉！<br />\n<br />\n條友焦土派?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec73ca70f395e2efcbe4ed8bf4a6263a5d278a8","tid":1105892,"uid":52459,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"發夢都無諗到，民賤聯同民賤聯b聯會一齊聯手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aeff12707ffbe453a1d976b1fdcee77710c5ab","tid":1105892,"uid":61589,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"cec73ca70f395e2efcbe4ed8bf4a6263a5d278a8","tid":1105892,"uid":52459,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"發夢都無諗到，民賤聯同民賤聯b聯會一齊聯手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T09:29: